title: Ben Elton - Live 1997
description:
Ben Elton performed to over 300,000 fans during his 1997 sell-out stand-up comedy tour around Britain and this show gives you the chance to listen to Ben's supreme gift for storytelling and observational comedy. 

I picked up this cassette in London years ago.  I listened to this rare recording last week and it still cracks me up.  I couldn't see any torrents of it anywhere so thought I'd rip it to mp3 files [side 1 & side 2] and upload.

Enjoy & Seed!
